    • Chore

      public Chore(int id, int userId, String name, String description, int reward, String home, String icon, LocalDate dueDate, boolean completed)
      Constructs a new Contact with the specified first name, last name, email, and phone number.
      Parameters:
      id - The identifier and primary key of chore
      userId - The identifier and primary key of user
      name - The name/ title of the chore
      description - The brief description of what's the chore
      reward - The reward in integer of on a chores completion
      home - The identifier of user's home
      icon - The name of the image on the chores entry
      dueDate - The due date of the chore
      completed - The status of the chore's completion
